#id=1
#text=After breakfast I got in my car and drove to the grocery store to buy food for the next several days .
#id=2
#text=I like to walk so I parked in the back row of the parking lot .
#id=3
#text=I walked in the store and selected a shopping cart that did n't have stuck wheels .
#id=4
#text=As I normally do I first proceeded to the deli department and got a number .
#id=5
#text=Since there were several people in front of me I started my shopping near the deli .
#id=6
#text=I picked some fresh produce and vegetables until my number was called .
#id=7
#text=At the deli I purchased ham , cheese and salami .
#id=8
#text=I picked up a whole chicken and a steak , the steak would be for tonight the chicken for a few days .
#id=9
#text=I picked up stuffing and gravy for the chicken .
#text=I browsed through the isles selecting various items that I did n't really need .
#text=As I proceeded to the checkout there was a sale isle which I picked up a few more items .
#text=I paid for my groceries and walked back to my car , placing the bags in the car and drove home .
